title: Weekend Crochet for Babies
description: Designed for all skill levels, this crafters companion features fun and versatile patterns for baby clothes through simple projects that can be completed in a weekend. Beginners will appreciate the instructions on getting started and essential techniques, while experienced crocheters will enjoy the range of different effects created in these garments, such as chunky textured fabric and delicate lacy patterns. These projects make use of a wide selection of yarns; can be easily adapted for infants or toddlers; include detailed information on stitches and techniques; and feature designs such as classic sweaters, tops for girls and boys, a duffle coat, a lacy cardigan, a hat and scarf set, booties, mittens, a dress, and two dolls.
